[These reports bring the total of human cases to 8; 7 in New York (6 in
Staten Island and one in Brooklyn), and one in Jersey City, the first case
outside the New York City area. The most recent 3 cases are all younger
than first 4 cases and infection appears to have occurred after the
initiation of mosquito control procedures. -Mod.CP
